# ESG dashboard

msgid "About the Project"
msgstr "About the Project"

msgid "project tagline"
msgstr "AI-powered ESG assessment for green finance in Central Asia."

msgid "project overview"
msgstr "NovdAI is an ESG (Environmental, Social, Governance) assessment platform. It analyses company reports and documents and produces objective ESG scores, key findings, material risks and actionable recommendations — helping banks, investors and companies make faster, more consistent green-finance decisions aligned with Uzbekistan’s national green taxonomy."

msgid "The problem"
msgstr "The problem"

msgid "project problem text"
msgstr "Green-finance decisions require ESG assessment, but manual review is slow, subjective and expensive. As Uzbekistan builds its national green taxonomy, banks and investors need a fast, consistent way to evaluate projects and companies against green criteria."

msgid "Our solution"
msgstr "Our solution"

msgid "project solution text"
msgstr "Upload a company report or paste text, and the platform evaluates it across all three ESG pillars in seconds — grounded in the document, in your language, with clear scores, material risks and recommendations you can act on."

msgid "How it works"
msgstr "How it works"

msgid "Upload"
msgstr "Upload"

msgid "project step1 desc"
msgstr "Upload a company report (PDF or image) or paste text."

msgid "AI analysis"
msgstr "AI analysis"

msgid "project step2 desc"
msgstr "The platform reads the document and evaluates Environmental, Social and Governance factors."

msgid "Get scores"
msgstr "Get scores"

msgid "project step3 desc"
msgstr "Receive E, S and G scores, an overall rating, key findings and risks."

msgid "Take action"
msgstr "Take action"

msgid "project step4 desc"
msgstr "Use the recommendations and saved history to make informed decisions."

msgid "Who it is for"
msgstr "Who it is for"

msgid "Banks"
msgstr "Banks"

msgid "project aud banks desc"
msgstr "Assess green-loan applications quickly and consistently."

msgid "Investors"
msgstr "Investors"

msgid "project aud investors desc"
msgstr "Screen companies and projects for ESG performance and risk."

msgid "Companies"
msgstr "Companies"

msgid "project aud companies desc"
msgstr "Understand and improve your own ESG standing."

msgid "Regulators"
msgstr "Regulators"

msgid "project aud regulators desc"
msgstr "Support green-taxonomy alignment and reporting."

